## URL Transformations

Build URLs with on-the-fly transformations.

```javascript
// Using cloudinary.url()
const url = cloudinary.url('products/my-image', {
  width: 400,
  height: 300,
  crop: 'fill',
  gravity: 'auto',
  quality: 'auto',
  fetch_format: 'auto',
});
