## Streaming (Language Models)

```typescript
const output = await replicate.stream(
  'meta/llama-2-70b-chat',
  {
    input: {
      prompt: 'Tell me a story about a robot',
      max_new_tokens: 500,
    },
  }
);

for await (const event of output) {
  process.stdout.write(event.data);
